Planned Features
----------------

 o Admin handler framework

 o Authentication/Authorization

 o More featureful backends
   * RDF metastore
   * High-performance filestore 

 o Utility scripts for switching filestores, metastores, mass-updates of 
   metadata, etc. 

 o Pretty jQuery+Ext-enabled interface
   * Search forms
   * Metadata grid view
   * Result galleries

 o Aggregate fetch
   * GET /metadata/«uuid1»,«uuid2»,«uuidn»
   * GET /«uuid1»,«uuid2»,«uuidn»

 * Duplicate checking via checksum comparison
   * What if the user is uploading the same file but with additional metadata?

 * Move the default #make_html_content method into the HTML filter, then reverse over
   the handlers that have run. If one of them implements #make_html_content itself,
   delegate to it, otherwise just do the inspect in the filter itself.

